<BaseLayout title="Freelance Mentor Program | FIRSTÂ® Alumni & Mentors Network at Michigan">
    <div class="container">
        <main class="content">
            <h1>Freelance Mentor Program</h1>
            <p class="text-par">
                The Freelance Mentor Program provides short-term mentoring
                resources to local teams of all levels. University of Michigan students 
                with expertise in areas such as chassis, electronics, programming, 
                presentations, and business plans are available assist teams on a case
                by case basis. Some notable examples include a day of autonomous
                mentoring for FRC team WARHBOTS (shown below), an afternoon of practice 
                match refereeing and practice judging sessions for the five Chelsea and 
                Dexter FTC teams, and a project presentation review and critique for FLL
                team The Robobears.
            </p>
            <p class="text-par">
                Looking for help? If you represent an FLL team, contact our FLL coordinator at
                <a href="mailto:famnm.fll@umich.edu">famnm.fll@umich.edu</a>.
                If you represent an FRC or FTC team, fill out the form linked below
                to request mentoring from FAMNM.
            </p>
            <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center my-4">
                <Link to="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdxwCNhkoOetBASDQuRNeuxTaVqER6vIT36LixpFXDfwyfEEA/viewform"
                    class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Request FRC or FTC mentoring&nbsp;&nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i></Link>
                <a href="mailto:famnm.fll@umich.edu"
                    class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact FLL coordinator&nbsp;&nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i></a>
            </div>
            <Picture attributes={{picture: {class: "img-fluid col-md-8 col-xs-12 d-inline-block", id: "freelance-img"}}} src="/img/teams/fr_mentor1.jpg" alt="FAMNM Freelance Mentoring"/>
            <p><b>Pictured: Freelance mentors helping out Team 6618 - WARHBOTS for <i>FIRST<sup>&reg;</sup></i> Power Up!</b></p>
        </main>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
